OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,7,Fsome bright or sunny spells. A cloudy
OL,8,Fstart in parts of the east. A warm
OL,9,Fday, but cooler along the Caithness
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be dry with lengthy
OL,15,Fclear periods. A warm night along the
OL,16,Fwest coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FDry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,19,FBecoming very warm, locally hot.
OL,20,FCooler along the Caithness coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
