OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand much cooler on Friday with some
OL,7,Fpatchy rain in the west, otherwise
OL,8,Fdry. Outbreaks of rain spreading east
OL,9,Fon Saturday followed by a few showers
OL,10,Fon Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
